name: Storm Area 51 Raid
description:
RAID AREA 51!
Embark on a thrilling quest to Area 51. They can't stop us all!

BUILD YOUR ARMY!
Recruit and level up your army of Ninja Runners, Kyles, Karens, Furries, and many more.

BRING HOME THE ALIENS!
Uncover the secrets of Area 51 and save your new alien friends.
